<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="113" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1009,1111]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,300,1009,1037]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Remarks –</emphasis>
Until now, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Garman" baseAuthorityYear="1883" box="[453,571,1009,1038]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="querci">
<emphasis box="[453,571,1009,1038]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">A. querci</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was only reported from the 
<collectingCountry box="[935,999,1009,1038]" name="United States of America" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">USA</collectingCountry>
on bur oak (
<taxonomicName authority="Michx." authorityName="Michx." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrocarpa">
<emphasis box="[1163,1436,1009,1038]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Quercus macrocarpa</emphasis>
Michx.
</taxonomicName>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Garman, H." box="[270,451,1046,1075]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" pagination="123 - 143" refId="ref3638" refString="Garman, H. (1883) The Phytopti and other injurious plant mites. 12 th Illinois Report, pp. 123 - 143." type="book chapter" year="1883">Garman 1883</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Briones, M. L. &amp; McDaniel, B." box="[464,839,1046,1075]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" pagination="1 - 123" refId="ref3327" refString="Briones, M. L. &amp; McDaniel, B. (1976) The eriophyid plant mites of South Dakota. South Dakota Agricultural Experiment Station Technical Bulletin, 43: 1 - 123." type="journal article" year="1976">Briones and McDaniel, 1976</bibRefCitation>
). The characteristics and habitus of the Iranian specimens are completely in consistent with what 
<bibRefCitation author="Briones, M. L. &amp; McDaniel, B." box="[794,1177,1082,1111]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113" pagination="1 - 123" refId="ref3327" refString="Briones, M. L. &amp; McDaniel, B. (1976) The eriophyid plant mites of South Dakota. South Dakota Agricultural Experiment Station Technical Bulletin, 43: 1 - 123." type="journal article" year="1976">Briones and McDaniel (1976)</bibRefCitation>
reported.
</paragraph>
